reviewText: Rita Rudner is one of the funniest Comediennes I've come across. She has great laugh out loud material that's clean but But she's a constant material repeater, Like DL Hughley, Earthquake And Bruce BruceThe Majority of the material she uses us mainly Re-hashed material from her 90's HBO specialsHBO One Night StandAndBorn to Be Mild.In a way, considering those specials have never been put onto DVD, it was a good idea to re-use the material but it's also a disappointment to us who have heard it before
